body:
FYI: Application Payment Submitted

An applicant has submitted payment for their membership dues. The treasurer will verify receipt and process activation.

APPLICANT INFORMATION:
Name: {{FULL_NAME}}
Membership Level: {{MEMBERSHIP_LEVEL}}
Household Type: {{HOUSEHOLD_TYPE}}
Application ID: {{APPLICATION_ID}}

PAYMENT DETAILS:
Payment Method: {{PAYMENT_METHOD}}
Payment Date Submitted: {{PAYMENT_DATE}}
Payment Reference: {{PAYMENT_REFERENCE}}
Amount: ${{DUES_USD}} USD / P{{DUES_BWP}} BWP

NEXT STEP:
The Treasurer will verify the payment receipt within 2 business days. Once verified, the member will be activated and this will be reported to the board.

No action is required from board members at this time.

GEA System

FYI: Application Approved for Security Review

The board has approved this application and it has been forwarded to the RSO (Regional Security Officer) for document verification.

APPLICANT INFORMATION:
Name: {{FULL_NAME}}
Membership Level: {{MEMBERSHIP_LEVEL}}
Household Type: {{HOUSEHOLD_TYPE}}
Application ID: {{APPLICATION_ID}}
Board Approval Date: {{BOARD_APPROVAL_DATE}}

STATUS:
Initial Board Review: APPROVED ✓
RSO Security Review: IN PROGRESS

TIMELINE:
The RSO typically completes document reviews within 3-5 business days. Once the RSO approves the documents, the application will return to the board for final approval.

No action is required from board members at this time.

GEA System

FYI: New Member Activated

Payment has been verified by the Treasurer and this applicant's membership is now ACTIVE. The application process is complete.

NEW MEMBER INFORMATION:
Name: {{FULL_NAME}}
Membership Level: {{MEMBERSHIP_LEVEL}}
Household Type: {{HOUSEHOLD_TYPE}}
Application ID: {{APPLICATION_ID}}

MEMBERSHIP STATUS: ACTIVE ✓

MEMBERSHIP DETAILS:
Membership Start Date: {{MEMBERSHIP_START_DATE}}
Membership Expiration: {{MEMBERSHIP_EXPIRATION_DATE}}
Payment Reference: {{PAYMENT_REFERENCE}}
Verification Date: {{VERIFICATION_DATE}}

WHAT THE MEMBER RECEIVED:
✓ Welcome email with complete facility access information
✓ Portal login and instructions
✓ Digital membership card (ready to download)
✓ Facility booking information and member benefits overview

MEMBER CAN NOW:
- Book GEA facilities (Tennis Court, Leobo, Playground, Gym)
- Attend GEA events and activities
- Access member-only services and discounts
- Download digital membership card
- Use all member portal features

The membership application process is complete. No further action required.

GEA System
